
= p2p-oriented art & cultural centre in Minsk, Belarus

URL = http://la-mora.info/

=Description=

""House of Culture 'La Mora' (la-mora.info). Now we are establishing more official formal organisation. We are working in wide-cultural spheres: music, theaters, art, cinema, cyber-activism, travelling, education. Our focuses - the grassroot culture,  self-organising groups of people who share their creativity to the same class (in Marx's meaning) of people. We also working on developing a network of cinema-lovers, underground musicians , etc. Our movement are trying to explore the borders between professional deal and amateur one. Also our activists are taking part in transdisciplinary events in Minsk: multidisciplinary hackathons, theatre experiments, festival, free open-source software movement, etc. There are a not a very big amount of people who takes part in all activities: but exist a core of activists."

